1000 Company Sourcing Proposal

Objective

Build a verified list of 1000 ICP-qualified specialty manufacturing companies within one month.

---

 Week 1 — Data Collection

Sources:

* LinkedIn
* IndiaMART
* StartupIndia
* TradeIndia
* Industry directories
* Government manufacturing databases

Expected output:
5000 raw company names.

---

 Week 2 — AI-Assisted Filtering

AI tools would be used to:

* Identify manufacturers
* Detect technical founders
* Identify growth signals
* Categorize companies by industry

Expected output:
2000 partially qualified companies.

---

Week 3 — Manual Verification & Quality Control

Activities:

* Website verification
* Removing traders/service firms
* Checking growth activity
* Validating manufacturing capability

Expected output:
1200 verified companies.

---

Week 4 — Final Qualification & Outreach Preparation

Activities:

* Federer scoring
* Prioritization
* Personalization hook creation
* CRM-ready formatting

Expected output:
1000 high-quality target companies.

---

 Quality Control Measures

To reduce false positives:

* Cross-source validation
* Manual verification
* Negative prompting while using AI
* Rechecking unsupported claims

---

 Conclusion

The combination of AI-assisted research and manual verification can significantly improve sourcing speed while maintaining quality and accuracy.
